oatmeal water
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:brose, a refreshment for shearers or outdoor workers, a mixture of water, sugar and oatmeal.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
